avApplMemManagerTotalNvRamSize.description: The total max size allowable of the Memory in KBytes.

avApplMemManagerTable.name: avApplMemManagerTable
avApplMemManagerTable.description: Table of different application and their memory allocation in the RAM and NvRAM.

avApplMemManagerEntry.name: avApplMemManagerEntry
avApplMemManagerEntry.description: An entry in the table, containing data about application and its memory type.

avApplMemManagerId.name: avApplMemManagerId
avApplMemManagerId.description: Index of the application. SNIFFER application index is 1. TFTP server application index is 2.

avApplMemManagerType.name: avApplMemManagerType
avApplMemManagerType.description: The Type of the memory that the application use. 1 - NvRAM, 2 - RAM.

avApplMemManagerName.name: avApplMemManagerName
avApplMemManagerName.description: The name of the application. For Sniffer application 'SNIFFER'. For TFTP Server Application 'TFTP Server'.

avApplMemManagerSize.name: avApplMemManagerSize
avApplMemManagerSize.description: The size of the Memory in KBytes for specific application and memory type.

avApplMemManagerMinSize.description: The Min size allowable of the Memory in KBytes for specific application and memory type.

avApplMemManagerMaxSize.description: The max size allowable of the Memory in KBytes for specific application and memory type.
